This is the LAST call!

You can expect all this and so much more yet to be revealed in Alliance Insight! Make sure to check back soon for more information.
Alliance Insight contains:
10 Secret Rares
14 Ultra Rares
26 Super Rares
50 Commons
(24 of these cards are also available as Quarter Century Secret Rare and 1 special card is ONLY available as a Quarter Century Secret Rare!)
